 然後先會回應<br />\n我尋日由7點留到12點 真系好唔想就甘放過佢地<br />\n香港人 加油 堅持 <br />\n<br />\n我知冇可能日日都去，但連續兩日去系必需，如果唔系就正中SHK高層下懷，我地根本就只系去一日打卡趁墟！聽日後日之後都可以唔再去，但今日，今日一定要再去，等佢地唔知究竟件事會維持幾耐，要佢地怕，佢地先會回應！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日，八點，不見不散！<br />\n希望大家，團結，堅持，<br />\n新地高層咪龜縮<br />\n否則商鋪冇人租！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf4666b0a79302efeb9eba7b479a6c6f17ad7451","tid":1325080,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"對抗一個極權政府<br />\n必定要全民皆兵"},{"pid":"df11a54e62135177f87b8632d060da581171dfe8","tid":1325080,"uid":216710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"859dec5bf52c31ac6acb9f16c1ea1fec715fa360","tid":1325080,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"全世界full gear"},{"pid":"5286732be18e3a926858a3de2ffbe2eb923a42d1","tid":1325080,"uid":48787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"721 去金鐘"},{"pid":"99bb05170b52b21a50b7d19f94aeb35177146831","tid":1325080,"uid":56277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdcf5844c5572a9344d76dc1e7a854bd6b1f5719","tid":1325080,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b91721177782547ea892646f344172bd9e0f7d3d","tid":1325080,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16aaf4d4be380c656632d5180e552317f20d6d44","tid":1325080,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"轉地圖再畫過 改左地點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7。21 港島見</span><br />\n請帶齊裝備<br />\n唔好再靜係帶口罩 要保護自己 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光 復 香 港 。 時 代 革 命 。 香 港 建 國</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1f9e501bd4a4ef6b4e25a4f820f6bcb3edacf11c","tid":1325080,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"